  22:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * è‹¥ن¸چéœ€è¦پهٹ¨و€پè°ƒو•´é‡ڈوµ‹هگ‘é‡ڈzï¼Œهڈ¯ç®€هچ•ه°†ç»“و‍„ن½“ن¸­çڑ„Use_Auto_Adjustmentهˆ‌ه§‹هŒ–ن
  23:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * ه§‹هŒ–çں©éکµPé‚£و ·ç”¨ه¸¸è§„و–¹ه¼ڈهˆ‌ه§‹هŒ–z H Rهچ³هڈ¯م€‚
  24:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * If automatic adjustment is not required, assign zero to the UseAutoAdjustment
  25:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * and initialize z H R in the normal way as matrix P.
  26:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  *
  27:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * è¦پو±‚é‡ڈوµ‹هگ‘é‡ڈzن¸ژوژ§هˆ¶هگ‘é‡ڈuهœ¨ن¼ و„ںه™¨ه›‍è°ƒه‡½و•°ن¸­و›´و–°م€‚و•´و•°0و„ڈه‘³ç‌€é‡ڈوµ‹و— 
  28:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * و»¤و³¢و›´و–°هگژو— ن¼ و„ںه™¨و•°وچ®و›´و–°م€‚ه› و­¤é‡ڈوµ‹هگ‘é‡ڈzن¸ژوژ§هˆ¶هگ‘é‡ڈuن¼ڑهœ¨هچ،ه°”و›¼و»¤و
  29:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * MeasuredVector and ControlVector are required to be updated in the sensor
  30:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * callback function. Integer 0 in measurement vector z indicates the invalidity
  31:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * of current measurement, so MeasuredVector and ControlVector will be reset
