  32:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * (to 0) during each update.
  33:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  *
  34:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * و­¤ه¤–ï¼Œçں©éکµPè؟‡ه؛¦و”¶و•›هگژو»¤و³¢ه™¨ه°†éڑ¾ن»¥ه†چé€‚ه؛”çٹ¶و€پçڑ„ç¼“و…¢هڈکهŒ–ï¼Œن»ژè€Œن؛§ç”ںو»
  35:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * é€ڑè؟‡é™گهˆ¶çں©éکµPوœ€ه°ڈه€¼çڑ„و–¹و³•ï¼Œهڈ¯وœ‰و•ˆوٹ‘هˆ¶و»¤و³¢ه™¨çڑ„è؟‡ه؛¦و”¶و•›ï¼Œè¯¦وƒ…è¯·è§پن¾
  36:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * Additionally, the excessive convergence of matrix P will make filter incapable
  37:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * of adopting the slowly changing state. This implementation can effectively
  38:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * suppress filter excessive convergence through boundary limiting for matrix P.
  39:modules/algorithm/kalman_filter.c ****  * For more details, please see the example.
